# The Docker build context is the repo root (issue #147, so the
# github-sdlc-planning MCP server's file: dependency on
# packages/singleflight-cache is actually present). This keeps that
# context lean: excludes are scoped the same way .gitignore's own /dist
# entry is (root-anchored, so plugins/*/mcp-server/dist and
# packages/*/dist — which the build genuinely needs — are never matched
# by the bare "dist" name here).
node_modules
.git
/dist
.astro
coverage
*.log
.env
.env.local
.DS_Store
*.tsbuildinfo
